title: Group Therapy: I'm Tired of Being Pushed Around
description: Amelia called the show today for Group Therapy. She's been struggling with being pushed around and used by her friends, co workers, & the people around her CONSTANTLY. She doesn't know what to do about it so we try our best to help her out! If you have any advice DM us @daveryanshow on Facebook / Instagram!
